## Фаза 4 — Буфер давления для завершённых штрихов

**IC_Stroke:**
```csharp
private void IC_Stroke(object sender, InkCollectorStrokeEventArgs e)
{
    if (Root.PressureSensitivity && Root.CurrentStrokePressure.Count > 0)
    {
        Root.StrokePressureData[e.Stroke.Id] =
            Root.CurrentStrokePressure.ToArray();
        Root.CurrentStrokePressure.Clear();
    }
    else if (Root.PressureSensitivity)
    {
        int pts = e.Stroke.PacketCount;
        float[] neutral = new float[pts];
        for (int i = 0; i < pts; i++) neutral[i] = 0.5f;
        Root.StrokePressureData[e.Stroke.Id] = neutral;
    }
    // ... существующий код ...
}
```

**Очистка при Undo/Clear:**
```csharp
Root.StrokePressureData.Remove(removedStroke.Id);
```

